name: MENE Regret (Lower is Better)
query: SELECT CAST(agent_name AS VARCHAR) AS id, mene_regret, mene_regret_se FROM results ORDER BY mene_regret ASC

name: Utilitarian Welfare
query: SELECT CAST(agent_name AS VARCHAR) AS id, uw_percent, uw_percent_se FROM results ORDER BY uw_percent DESC

name: Nash Welfare
query: SELECT CAST(agent_name AS VARCHAR) AS id, nw_percent, nw_percent_se FROM results ORDER BY nw_percent DESC

name: Nash Welfare Adjusted
query: SELECT CAST(agent_name AS VARCHAR) AS id, nwa_percent, nwa_percent_se FROM results ORDER BY nwa_percent DESC

name: Envy-Free (EF1)
query: SELECT CAST(agent_name AS VARCHAR) AS id, ef1_percent, ef1_percent_se FROM results ORDER BY ef1_percent DESC
